<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday XYZ ✈️</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1931,#185adb,#43c6ac);
    overflow:hidden;
}

.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:700px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:25px;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
}

h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    color:#FFD700;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

h2{
    font-size:1.8rem;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

p{
    font-size:1.15rem;
    line-height:1.8;
    margin:15px 0;
}

.quote{
    color:#FFE082;
    font-style:italic;
    font-size:1.25rem;
    margin:20px 0;
}

.plane{
    font-size:70px;
    animation:fly 4s infinite ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes fly{
    0%{
        transform:translateX(-25px) rotate(-10deg);
    }
    50%{
        transform:translateX(25px) rotate(10deg);
    }
    100%{
        transform:translateX(-25px) rotate(-10deg);
    }
}

button{
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    background:#FFD700;
    color:#000;
    font-size:18px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:0.3s;
}

button:hover{
    transform:scale(1.08);
}

footer{
    margin-top:25px;
    opacity:0.8;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="plane">✈️</div>

    <h1>Happy Birthday 🎂</h1>

    <h2>XYZ ❤️</h2>

    <p>
        Today is all about celebrating an amazing girl who dares to dream big.
    </p>

    <p>
        As an <b>Aviation Trainee</b>, you are preparing to conquer the skies.
        Every lesson you learn and every challenge you overcome brings you
        one step closer to your dreams.
    </p>

    <div class="quote">
        "Dear XYZ, the sky is not your limit—it's your playground."
    </div>

    <p>
        Keep dreaming fearlessly, keep believing in yourself,
        and never let setbacks dim your shine.
        The world belongs to those who have the courage to chase their dreams.
    </p>

    <p>
        May this birthday bring you happiness, success, and endless opportunities.
        One day you'll fly higher than you ever imagined,
        and everyone will look up and say,
        <b>"That's XYZ, the girl who turned her dreams into reality."</b>
    </p>

    <button onclick="showWish()">🎁 Open Birthday Wish</button>

    <footer>
        Made with ❤️ for XYZ
    </footer>

</div>

<script>
function showWish(){
    alert(
`🎂 HAPPY BIRTHDAY XYZ! ✈️

May your dreams soar beyond the clouds,
your courage stay stronger than turbulence,
and your future shine brighter than the stars.

Keep flying, Dreamer! ❤️`
    );
}
</script>

</body>
</html>